         </div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a1"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... in the <hi>Trayastriṃśa</hi> [heaven], (in the town) Sudarśana ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... the Buddha heard [it] ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... when ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a4"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... the Buddha, the teacher, ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a5"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... having become. Not ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b2"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b3"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... you (?) ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b4"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... births ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b5"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... and carrying out ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b6"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... says: «So it will be!»</seg></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
